<template id="template.widgets.clock.desc">
    The Time &amp; Date widget displays the current time and date for either the local timezone or any other timezone.<br />
    <br />
    No setup is required for this widget, however you can select a timezone using the settings menu.  You can also choose to display a 24 hour or analog clock via the settings menu.<br />
    <br />
    Variations:<br />
    <br />
    Tiny: Displays the current time in either a 12 hour, 24 hour or analog clock format.<br />
    Small: Displays the current time in either a 12 hour, 24 hour or analog clock format and the date in the selected timezone.
</template>
